Rating: 4
I was surprised at how tasty this was. I used broccoli instead of zucchini and just before serving, tossed in the juice of half a lemon, a couple tablespoons of freshly chopped basil, halved grape tomatoes and fresh mozzerella (the tiny-sized balls). Super tasty and satisfying!

